## Syntax highlighting for Hoverfly

syntax hoverfly "\.(hf/fly)$"
comment "::"

#arrows
color brightcyan "(<=|=>)"

#imports
color italic,lightblue "^[ ]*<= .*$"

#variables
color bold,lagoon "(#|\^|&|!)[ ]*\-?[0-9]+"

#pointer marker
color brightred "PTR"

#strings
color cyan ""([^"\]|\\.)*"|""""

#trailing whitespace
color ,green "[ ]+$"

#comments
color white "^[ ]*::.*$"

